params._protocolAssetAmount: amount of protocol asset to deposit

packFeederParams(uint256).notice: pack all feeder params into a struct

seedPools(uint256,uint256,uint256,(int25.notice: seed liquidity in core uniswap pools- deposit asset and numeraire into vault, mint halfPerp and onePerp- deposit onePerp into twoCrab, receiving twoCrab and twoPerp- deposit halfPerp into halfCrab, receiving halfCrab and onePerp- create four Uniswap LPs: zeroPerp/numeraire, onePerp/asset, halfCrab/numeraire, twoCrab/numeraire- deposit onePerp/asset LP into assetFlo and the remaining LPs into stableFlo- deposit stableFlo, assetFlo, and any other remaining tokens into vault
